name: Voyager II
description:
Play as the Voyager II probe, explore a reconstruction of the solar system,

the game has simple graphics, but no limits you can go as far as you want, although you won't find anything more,

 otherwise try to approach the planets without hitting them, take pictures and send them to earth to complete the tasks.

the game currently contains 8 planets, pluto, the sun, the moon, an asteroid and a com satellite.

You can control the probe with an AZERTY or QWERTY keyboard or with the directional arrows, the photo button must be clicked with a mouse (or finger if the screen is touch-sensitive).

created by Sebcool66
